snippet.title: Twinsanity: Omicron - Reveal Trailer | PC, Android
snippet.description:
The story continues. Twinsanity is back in his timeline after defeating Time Shadow and taking his Relic of Time. But this is not where the evil ends. Two days after the events of “Trapped in Time”, Twinsanity figures out that someone wants his power. Who? How? Why?

"Twinsanity: Omicron" is the second installment in Twinsanity's Game Series. The game is still in development but you can still try the DEMO version. Enjoy it.
https://gamejolt.com/games/twinsanity_omicron_demo/479627

If you like this trailer press the "Like" button and subscribe to my channel for more videos.
